<p begin="121300000t" end="136400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">这下就5连胜了</p>
<p begin="139600000t" end="164000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">这下就10连败了</p>
<p begin="195600000t" end="215100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">你的运气到底有多差啊</p>
<p begin="222500000t" end="245900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">这可是我盼了好久的修学旅行</p>
<p begin="251100000t" end="267900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">已经结束了</p>
<p begin="271400000t" end="302800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">不 这都还没开始呢</p>
<p begin="302800000t" end="324800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">玩游戏输了而已 太夸张了</p>
<p begin="327300000t" end="358300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">就是就是 人家偏偏就喜欢你一个人</p>
<p begin="358300000t" end="377600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">反而应该感到高兴吧</p>
<p begin="380700000t" end="413100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">那就开始下一局对战吧</p>
<p begin="459700000t" end="488800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">被狂龙王喜欢可高兴不起来</p>
<p begin="518300000t" end="547900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">虽说艾尔莎德是曾经的敌人</p>
<p begin="547900000t" end="579400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">但被践踏成这样就有点让人同情了</p>
<p begin="595000000t" end="631500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">这是魔法学者维达 勇者莉迪娅</p>
<p begin="634400000t" end="661300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">怎样才能把她们刻画成这样啊</p>
<p begin="667300000t" end="721300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">算了 历史嘛 被夸大和美化很正常吧</p>
<p begin="858600000t" end="870500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">怎…怎么了</p>
<p begin="870500000t" end="884100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">好像不太对劲</p>
<p begin="886700000t" end="901500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">这恐怕是…</p>
<p begin="975500000t" end="998300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">亚德 这是…</p>
<p begin="1001800000t" end="1011500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">嗯</p>
<p begin="1016900000t" end="1029500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">欢迎你们</p>
<p begin="1039400000t" end="1058200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">被选中的各位</p>
<p begin="1217700000t" end="1250500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">足以融化孤独的呼声</p>
<p begin="1250500000t" end="1288800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">究竟来自于何人？</p>
<p begin="1294900000t" end="1339100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">向往着温暖 我出发了。</p>
<p begin="1339100000t" end="1356500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">再来，再来，再来！</p>
<p begin="1361300000t" end="1378300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">咏唱 交个朋友</p>
<p begin="1378300000t" end="1394700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">解除 扑克脸</p>
<p begin="1394700000t" end="1426100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">平起平坐的坦诚交谈</p>
<p begin="1427700000t" end="1445300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">打破墙壁吧 用转移魔法</p>
<p begin="1445300000t" end="1461300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">瞬间便融洽相处</p>
<p begin="1461300000t" end="1477400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">共鸣之和谐 打破孤独</p>
<p begin="1477400000t" end="1491100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">精准无比 太完美了吧？</p>
<p begin="1491100000t" end="1554600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">沉默寡言的挑战者 迈出第一步</p>
<p begin="1554600000t" end="1608500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">生涩的自己也要抱紧</p>
<p begin="1612400000t" end="1646500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">一起开始尝试！就是现在 尝试！</p>
<p begin="1649800000t" end="1687900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">向奇迹发起挑战吧</p>
<p begin="1687900000t" end="1728200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">将无敌的心情连结到底</p>
<p begin="1728200000t" end="1745200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">放马过来 放马过来</p>
<p begin="1745200000t" end="1779000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">鼓足干劲 尝试！发展超乎想像</p>
<p begin="1781500000t" end="1813300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">点燃勇气</p>
<p begin="1813300000t" end="1852800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">即使现在相隔遥远</p>
<p begin="1852800000t" end="1887200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">有朝一日 也必定能相互理解</p>
<p begin="1887200000t" end="1902900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">做我的朋友！！！</p>
<p begin="1902900000t" end="1956200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">哔哩哔哩译制<br />Translated by bilibili</p>
<p begin="1988700000t" end="2017900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">你是魔族吗</p>
<p begin="2022700000t" end="2048800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">人类会对未知事物冠以「魔」的名字</p>
<p begin="2053100000t" end="2081600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">按照这个定义 我或许也算是「魔族」</p>
<p begin="2092000000t" end="2112100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">但是 如果着眼本质</p>
<p begin="2112100000t" end="2129900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">那我就不是「魔族」</p>
<p begin="2134000000t" end="2149000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">那你到底是什么</p>
<p begin="2155400000t" end="2189200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">如果用你们的语言来表现</p>
<p begin="2200700000t" end="2227600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">称我为「神」或许比较恰当</p>
<p begin="2289400000t" end="2329300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">神？暂且当你是神好了</p>
<p begin="2334200000t" end="2366100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">那你想让我们干什么呢</p>
<p begin="2373200000t" end="2416700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">世界无穷无尽 未来与过去也在无限重复上演</p>
<p begin="2421100000t" end="2443200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">逝去的时间不复返</p>
<p begin="2448500000t" end="2481300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">但是那个人想颠覆这个法则</p>
<p begin="2481300000t" end="2518800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">想超越命运 改变世界的构造</p>
<p begin="2526200000t" end="2545000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">那个人与「魔王」的邂逅</p>
<p begin="2554100000t" end="2576900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">会剧烈撼动你的世界</p>
<p begin="2576900000t" end="2593290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">你与那人之间 必将消失一个</p>
<p begin="2598500000t" end="2646700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">不好意思 可以用我们能听懂的话解释吗</p>
<p begin="2666200000t" end="2700200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">我想请你们除掉「那个人」</p>
<p begin="2731300000t" end="2761400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">我希望 留下来的那个是你</p>
<p begin="2792200000t" end="2817300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">好了 一路顺风</p>
<p begin="2884200000t" end="2894700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">这里是？</p>
<p begin="2905500000t" end="2921400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">那是…</p>
<p begin="2976100000t" end="3011500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">这可真是万万没想到</p>
<p begin="3019700000t" end="3067000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">看样子我们被传送到古代世界了</p>
<p begin="3070200000t" end="3091300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">来…来到了古代世界…</p>
<p begin="3091300000t" end="3114600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">你是怎么知道的</p>
<p begin="3117800000t" end="3146100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">你们也看见了 天上有两个月亮</p>
<p begin="3150800000t" end="3180100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">在我们所处的世界 这是不可能出现的景象</p>
<p begin="3186400000t" end="3223200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">在过去 月亮因为某件事变成了一个</p>
<p begin="3231400000t" end="3251100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">因为古代发生的某件事</p>
<p begin="3265300000t" end="3289400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">于是你就认定我们被传送到古代了吗</p>
<p begin="3291900000t" end="3319900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">是的 根据周围的景象来看</p>
<p begin="3327500000t" end="3362500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">这里应该是「魔王」巴尔巴托斯陛下统治的大国</p>
<p begin="3365500000t" end="3400400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">瓦尔迪亚帝国的马奇纳地区</p>
<p begin="3413200000t" end="3441900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">不过前提是我没记错</p>
<p begin="3449300000t" end="3474000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">魔王陛下统治的时代</p>
<p begin="3474000000t" end="3502300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">你说魔王陛下…这么说来刚才…</p>
<p begin="3505700000t" end="3548500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">嗯 根据那个自称神明的人所描述的来看</p>
<p begin="3553900000t" end="3591400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">在这世界…存在着「魔王」陛下</p>
<p begin="3603700000t" end="3637400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">综上所述 可以推测出只要觐见「魔王」陛下</p>
<p begin="3641000000t" end="3666800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">状况就能有所发展</p>
<p begin="3679200000t" end="3703400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">觐见…魔王陛下？</p>
<p begin="3706300000t" end="3735400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">而那个自称神明的孩子</p>
<p begin="3735400000t" end="3760300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">要求我们除掉「那个人」</p>
<p begin="3763600000t" end="3783800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">如果能办到 或许…</p>
<p begin="3792700000t" end="3814800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">就能回到原来的时代对吧</p>
<p begin="3831500000t" end="3866200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">所以 我们当下的目标</p>
<p begin="3866200000t" end="3897800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">就是与「魔王」陛下见面 再除掉「那个人」</p>
<p begin="3911900000t" end="3931700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">看来就是这两个目标啊</p>
<p begin="3935400000t" end="3964200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">可是 他只说要除掉「那个人」</p>
<p begin="3964200000t" end="3982100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">根本没有线索啊</p>
<p begin="4005200000t" end="4048200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">觐见「魔王」陛下 这是首要目标没错</p>
<p begin="4052400000t" end="4063000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">可是…</p>
<p begin="4175400000t" end="4191200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">妈的</p>
<p begin="4209800000t" end="4219300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">那是什么</p>
<p begin="4219300000t" end="4250600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">十有八九是死亡刺蝎吧</p>
<p begin="4250600000t" end="4264600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">那是死亡刺蝎？</p>
<p begin="4264600000t" end="4291200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">跟我们认识的完全不同啊</p>
<p begin="4378100000t" end="4401300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">或许是多管闲事</p>
<p begin="4401300000t" end="4419400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">但还是去帮帮忙吧</p>
<p begin="4655600000t" end="4695300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">一…一招就干掉了死亡刺蝎吗</p>
<p begin="4741600000t" end="4756700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">亚德同学就是厉害</p>
<p begin="4770400000t" end="4795600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">亚德出马 简直小菜一碟</p>
<p begin="4847900000t" end="4873800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">你小子还挺有本事的嘛</p>
<p begin="4887100000t" end="4920300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">你救了我的部下 多谢了</p>
<p begin="4929400000t" end="4943000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">奥利维安女士</p>
<p begin="4956100000t" end="4991900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">你们是什么人 我们以前在哪里见过吗</p>
<p begin="4996400000t" end="5011500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">呃 就是…</p>
<p begin="5011500000t" end="5033900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">我们是 那个…</p>
<p begin="5039800000t" end="5056500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">真是万分抱歉</p>
<p begin="5059900000t" end="5104000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">您名震天下 她们对您怀有敬仰和憧憬之情</p>
<p begin="5108300000t" end="5141300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">所以才会表现得过度亲昵</p>
<p begin="5145800000t" end="5165990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">还请您宽宏大量</p>
<p begin="5165990000t" end="5175000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">哦？</p>
<p begin="5320800000t" end="5338100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">不为所动吗</p>
<p begin="5338100000t" end="5361500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">是的 这点程度还不至于</p>
<p begin="5364700000t" end="5384800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">好吧 跟我走</p>
<p begin="5470800000t" end="5490700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">怎…怎么说呢</p>
<p begin="5559000000t" end="5593300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">我们好像真的置身于传说之中</p>
<p begin="5634800000t" end="5657000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">你们好像对城里的状况很感兴趣啊</p>
<p begin="5679900000t" end="5726000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">是的 因为我们很久没来这里了</p>
<p begin="5729700000t" end="5750800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">你小子叫什么</p>
<p begin="5754300000t" end="5776300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">我名叫亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="5781300000t" end="5817900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">奥利维安女士为何要带我们来这里呢</p>
<p begin="5821100000t" end="5837500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">我就直说了</p>
<p begin="5842100000t" end="5872000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">亚德·梅特奥尔 加入我军吧</p>
<p begin="5888800000t" end="5923100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">你也知道 现在是群雄割据的时代</p>
<p begin="5928800000t" end="5969000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">外敌 也就是天外来客入侵了这个世界</p>
<p begin="5976200000t" end="6004100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">后来 他们创造出的魔族</p>
<p begin="6004100000t" end="6044000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">与我们人类的大战日益激化</p>
<p begin="6052100000t" end="6075400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">而能够左右战争走向的</p>
<p begin="6075400000t" end="6119900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">正是我们的国王巴尔巴托斯开发的人类用魔法</p>
<p begin="6125800000t" end="6165300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">据我观察 你的魔法相当熟练</p>
<p begin="6170800000t" end="6201100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">而且不咏唱就有那么大的威力</p>
<p begin="6211600000t" end="6237100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">你足以成为我军的中坚力量</p>
<p begin="6248500000t" end="6258300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">原来如此</p>
<p begin="6262600000t" end="6308300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">反过来说 不能放任拥有这种力量的人在外 对吗</p>
<p begin="6323300000t" end="6344000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">我有两个条件</p>
<p begin="6358000000t" end="6367100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">说来听听</p>
<p begin="6370700000t" end="6411400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">第一个是允许伊莉娜和金妮加入军队</p>
<p begin="6411400000t" end="6423100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">- 亚德同学<br />- 亚德</p>
<p begin="6423100000t" end="6441600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">急着送死吗</p>
<p begin="6445600000t" end="6467800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">我必定会保护好她们的</p>
<p begin="6470600000t" end="6494000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">那么 另一个条件是？</p>
<p begin="6499800000t" end="6544100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">请将我们分配到维达女士的直属部队</p>
<p begin="6544100000t" end="6557100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">维达？</p>
<p begin="6560800000t" end="6600700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">你小子明白自己在说什么吗</p>
<p begin="6600700000t" end="6622200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">嗯 那是自然</p>
<p begin="6634400000t" end="6644900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">您意下如何呢</p>
<p begin="6660000000t" end="6711300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">你有如此强的战斗能力 竟然想去后勤部队</p>
<p begin="6714300000t" end="6748400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">别看我们这样 其实还是学习中的魔法学者</p>
<p begin="6751600000t" end="6780700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">而且最主要的是我们没有野心</p>
<p begin="6783600000t" end="6827200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">她的部队里的确有一大半是学者和研究者</p>
<p begin="6830700000t" end="6866800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">不适合上阵杀敌 主要任务是补给和医疗</p>
<p begin="6872800000t" end="6905400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">在军队中的死亡率也远低于其他部队</p>
<p begin="6909600000t" end="6940300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">只要您答应这两个条件</p>
<p begin="6943200000t" end="6976000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">我们即刻起便能为陛下效力</p>
<p begin="6991400000t" end="7002400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">好吧</p>
<p begin="7007500000t" end="7044900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">我以我的权限 安排你们去她的直属部队</p>
<p begin="7056700000t" end="7102500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">这里就是魔法学者维达女士的研究所</p>
<p begin="7107700000t" end="7140200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">我们要被分配到这里对吧</p>
<p begin="7144200000t" end="7159200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">只要加入这家伙的部队</p>
<p begin="7159200000t" end="7190400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">她们遇上危险的概率就低多了</p>
<p begin="7193900000t" end="7218400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">我们想在这个时代活动</p>
<p begin="7218400000t" end="7248900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">待在维达手下是最安全的</p>
<p begin="7255800000t" end="7275800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">可惜遗憾至极</p>
<p begin="7347100000t" end="7359200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">平息了？</p>
<p begin="7359200000t" end="7372800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">是出事故了吗</p>
<p begin="7377500000t" end="7393600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">你们太天真了</p>
<p begin="7393600000t" end="7420000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">真正的地狱才刚刚开始</p>
<p begin="7441000000t" end="7461700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">大获成功</p>
<p begin="7465100000t" end="7506200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">不愧是我 这次的实验也很完美</p>
<p begin="7519100000t" end="7545700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">哦？好可爱的客人啊</p>
<p begin="7550500000t" end="7566500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">刚才那下看见了吗</p>
<p begin="7566500000t" end="7598700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">我的天才实力又爆发了</p>
<p begin="7598700000t" end="7627300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">物理层面也爆发了 说笑的</p>
<p begin="7652500000t" end="7677600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">不是 那个 没问题吗</p>
<p begin="7681000000t" end="7703600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">把研究所炸得支离破碎的</p>
<p begin="7708100000t" end="7724800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">维达女士会生气吧</p>
<p begin="7724800000t" end="7765900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">这是家常便饭啦 不生气不生气</p>
<p begin="7769000000t" end="7790800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">话说你们找我有事吗</p>
<p begin="7793900000t" end="7815300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">我们是来找维达女士的</p>
<p begin="7818600000t" end="7840300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">如果她在 可以帮忙叫一下她吗</p>
<p begin="7840300000t" end="7860300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">首先她得还活着才行</p>
<p begin="7863600000t" end="7885900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">你们在说什么呢</p>
<p begin="7885900000t" end="7905900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">维达不就在这里吗</p>
<p begin="7909600000t" end="7916800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">啊？</p>
<p begin="7924000000t" end="7938500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">我是维达</p>
<p begin="7941500000t" end="7968500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">我是天才美少女魔法学者</p>
<p begin="7971700000t" end="7980900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">懂了吗</p>
<p begin="8080100000t" end="8103100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">啊？</p>
<p begin="8107000000t" end="8133600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">真是的 太没礼貌了吧</p>
<p begin="8133600000t" end="8171900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">不能以貌取人 父母没教过你们吗</p>
<p begin="8175000000t" end="8189000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">可这…</p>
<p begin="8189000000t" end="8206200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">未免差太多了</p>
<p begin="8211900000t" end="8231600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">总之 你们等一下</p>
<p begin="8231600000t" end="8251200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">我这就把研究所变回去</p>
<p begin="8267600000t" end="8312700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">哦？居然想来我手下 真稀奇啊</p>
<p begin="8315300000t" end="8341200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">难道说 你们是我的死忠粉？</p>
<p begin="8360100000t" end="8382700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">属于我的时代终于来了吗</p>
<p begin="8382700000t" end="8415800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">那孩子真的是维达女士啊</p>
<p begin="8415800000t" end="8444400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">至…至今依然不敢相信</p>
<p begin="8448000000t" end="8467300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">或者说是不愿相信</p>
<p begin="8473400000t" end="8510500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">总之 我已经知道你们是奥利维安介绍来的了</p>
<p begin="8516200000t" end="8548100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">说吧 不止这一个理由吧</p>
<p begin="8563600000t" end="8600700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">那么 请容我表明我们的来历</p>
<p begin="8636400000t" end="8667200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">未来？你们是从未来来的？</p>
<p begin="8667200000t" end="8693900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">真的吗？真的 真的啊</p>
<p begin="8696600000t" end="8722800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">既不是「天外来客」也不是「古神」</p>
<p begin="8722800000t" end="8757000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">有别于两者的超高次元存在的尾巴我倒是抓住了</p>
<p begin="8757000000t" end="8786700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">但我没想到能以这种形式得到证实</p>
<p begin="8786700000t" end="8826500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">不得了 我现在激动得要死</p>
<p begin="8831100000t" end="8842500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">那个…</p>
<p begin="8842500000t" end="8859600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">维达女士…</p>
<p begin="8863500000t" end="8878500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">差点忘了 差点忘了</p>
<p begin="8884900000t" end="8908200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">总之 你们的情况我明白了</p>
<p begin="8908200000t" end="8932600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">就由我来庇护你们吧</p>
<p begin="8937200000t" end="8964300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">顺便帮助你们返回原来的时代吧</p>
<p begin="8964300000t" end="8976800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">太好了</p>
<p begin="8981400000t" end="9000500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">只不过 相对的</p>
<p begin="9049700000t" end="9059100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">完蛋</p>
<p begin="9064400000t" end="9079400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">希…希尔菲？</p>
<p begin="9079400000t" end="9104800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">等等 看起来不太对劲</p>
<p begin="9118200000t" end="9134300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">找到你了</p>
<p begin="9134300000t" end="9157600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">你跑不掉了 笨蛋</p>
<p begin="9164600000t" end="9194200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">这次你就乖乖死心吧</p>
<p begin="9217100000t" end="9243300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">快动手 莉迪姐姐</p>
<p begin="9373700000t" end="9384600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">莉迪娅…</p>
<p begin="9464000000t" end="9486800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">那就是传说中的…</p>
<p begin="9489700000t" end="9501800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">勇者</p>
<p begin="9523000000t" end="9539800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">维达 你这混蛋</p>
<p begin="9545100000t" end="9573900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">跟你说了后勤人手不够</p>
<p begin="9573900000t" end="9597200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">你他妈是没把我放眼里吗</p>
<p begin="9597200000t" end="9617300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">给我把部队规模扩大一倍</p>
<p begin="9617300000t" end="9670700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">否则我就找棍从你菊花捅到你脑袋去 混蛋</p>
<p begin="9682500000t" end="9712200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">别激动 冷静下来 莉迪娅</p>
<p begin="9716500000t" end="9744500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">我觉得后勤部队的人手很合适啊</p>
<p begin="9747200000t" end="9759600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">都 说 了</p>
<p begin="9759600000t" end="9798000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">危险的敌人就快出现了 听不懂啊</p>
<p begin="9798000000t" end="9825400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">我的直觉有强烈的反应</p>
<p begin="9860200000t" end="9887900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">这样吧 你把那边的三个人带走吧</p>
<p begin="9895800000t" end="9917900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">啊？那边是哪边…</p>
<p begin="9995000000t" end="10009300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">小妹妹 你叫什么</p>
<p begin="10017400000t" end="10031800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">我…我吗</p>
<p begin="10031800000t" end="10052100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">我…我叫金妮</p>
<p begin="10058500000t" end="10071500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">怎么样 小妹妹</p>
<p begin="10075200000t" end="10121100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">要不要立刻去我的别墅 与我共度梦幻般的时光</p>
<p begin="10128000000t" end="10155400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">这…这是 什…什么意思…</p>
<p begin="10163200000t" end="10183600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">你这反应…莫非…</p>
<p begin="10199500000t" end="10231000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">不是吧 身为魅魔居然还没经历过</p>
<p begin="10231000000t" end="10250000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">什么情况 这也太棒了吧</p>
<p begin="10274300000t" end="10289700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">干 干什么…</p>
<p begin="10289700000t" end="10310800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">你这屁股不错啊</p>
<p begin="10314700000t" end="10332500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">小妹妹</p>
<p begin="10342700000t" end="10370200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">等等 那…那里不行…</p>
<p begin="10391490000t" end="10403500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">亚德同学</p>
<p begin="10408300000t" end="10424700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">你干什么啊 混蛋</p>
<p begin="10424700000t" end="10448300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">真是非常抱歉</p>
<p begin="10448300000t" end="10479700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">我们才刚到这个城市</p>
<p begin="10482700000t" end="10510400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">她们也非常累了</p>
<p begin="10510400000t" end="10544600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">所以 还请自重 各方面都需要自重</p>
<p begin="10544600000t" end="10557400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">混蛋</p>
<p begin="10557400000t" end="10582000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">别他妈妨碍别人的恋情啊</p>
<p begin="10582000000t" end="10611900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">恋情？是性犯罪才对吧？</p>
<p begin="10611900000t" end="10644800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">啊？欠打是吧？</p>
<p begin="10644800000t" end="10664500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">出去单挑 混蛋</p>
<p begin="10677000000t" end="10690400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">行啊</p>
<p begin="10719700000t" end="10728600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">亚德</p>
<p begin="10728600000t" end="10738500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">亚德同学</p>
<p begin="10777200000t" end="10799000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">你们就在这里等着吧</p>
<p begin="11355000000t" end="11372200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">你这人啊…</p>
<p begin="11384000000t" end="11421400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">还是老样子 本性烂到家了</p>
<p begin="11421400000t" end="11451200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">啊？你说什么鸡巴 混蛋</p>
<p begin="11454100000t" end="11463300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">啊？</p>
<p begin="11981600000t" end="11991600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">妈的</p>
<p begin="12016500000t" end="12029700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">有两下子啊</p>
<p begin="12038000000t" end="12093500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">没有…想像中…厉害嘛…</p>
<p begin="12103100000t" end="12116800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">你这人…</p>
<p begin="12126700000t" end="12167900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">脸被揍成这样还嘴硬 没说服力啊</p>
<p begin="12177100000t" end="12222900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">你的脸还不是一样 都快跟哥布林一样了</p>
<p begin="12229000000t" end="12242300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">真是活该</p>
<p begin="12299000000t" end="12322100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">真是个讨厌的时代</p>
<p begin="12322100000t" end="12345100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">好想早点回现代</p>
<p begin="12351400000t" end="12381300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">你还真是个有趣的家伙</p>
<p begin="12389500000t" end="12406100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">你是叫亚德对吧？</p>
<p begin="12410200000t" end="12440200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">你带上那两个人来我这当后勤吧</p>
<p begin="12448800000t" end="12477300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">其实我很想让你上前线</p>
<p begin="12481600000t" end="12497800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">不过你有隐情吧</p>
<p begin="12501700000t" end="12530100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">否则怎么可能跑去当维达的手下</p>
<p begin="12538200000t" end="12561200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">既然你能看得这么透彻</p>
<p begin="12564200000t" end="12586200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">那就不要强人所难了</p>
<p begin="12605800000t" end="12633400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">我需要你的力量</p>
<p begin="12724800000t" end="12754800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">别让我说这么清楚啊 怪难为情的</p>
<p begin="12775600000t" end="12797100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">我可以求你一件事吗</p>
<p begin="12797100000t" end="12807600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">什么事</p>
<p begin="12807600000t" end="12840400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">我听说您与陛下的交情很好</p>
<p begin="12840400000t" end="12874000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">可否向陛下引荐我们呢</p>
<p begin="12877100000t" end="12893300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">你想见那家伙吗</p>
<p begin="12897900000t" end="12906200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">是的</p>
<p begin="12913900000t" end="12931700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">我倒是没问题</p>
<p begin="12935300000t" end="12969000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">但有我介入 他肯定会很牴触</p>
<p begin="12972800000t" end="12985300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">确实</p>
<p begin="12991600000t" end="13003900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">要是想见他</p>
<p begin="13008400000t" end="13038800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">就好好表现 赢得他的信任</p>
<p begin="13045600000t" end="13074000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">他会对信任的人敞开心扉的</p>
<p begin="13099400000t" end="13111000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">好吧</p>
<p begin="13115600000t" end="13134400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">好 那就定了</p>
<p begin="13429900000t" end="13508200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">超乎想像的未来正等待你发现</p>
<p begin="13508200000t" end="13572600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">打开大门的钥匙就在心中</p>
<p begin="13627300000t" end="13696600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">只要伸出你的手</p>
<p begin="13696600000t" end="13743700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">连未来都能改变</p>
<p begin="13743700000t" end="13814300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">冲动 渴望 重新开始</p>
<p begin="13821300000t" end="13868100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">若是转世重生 不要心存畏惧</p>
<p begin="13868100000t" end="13909800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">向甜美的过去告别</p>
<p begin="13913800000t" end="13960600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">在这日渐昏暗的世界</p>
<p begin="13960600000t" end="13993100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">随波逐流所无法掌握的自由</p>
<p begin="13993100000t" end="14046100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">去追求它吧</p>
<p begin="14050800000t" end="14082300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">舍弃孤独的强大</p>
<p begin="14084400000t" end="14119600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">追求相互理解的温暖</p>
<p begin="14119600000t" end="14154000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">将找到的那道光</p>
<p begin="14154000000t" end="14191600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">轻抱在怀里前行吧</p>
